==Hebrew==
===Verb===
;Qal construction
'''אָבֹד''', ''v.i.''
#be [[pressed]]
#go around in [[despair]]
#be [[lost]], [[perish]]
#be beyond recognition
#to be given up

====Participle====
# [[lost]], [[irretrievable]], [[perishing]], [[decayed]].
# ''Nif'al construction, v.i.'', be [[lost]], [[perish]].
# ''Piel construction, v.t.'', [[waste]], [[lose]], [[forfeit]], [[destroy]].
# ''Piel construction, v.t.'', to drop from [[memory]], to [[forget]].

===Adjective===
'''אָבֵד''', {{m}}
#[[perishable]], [[irretrievable]]

